title: Eating Crispy Chips
description:
Welcome to episode 63 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today we present our first eating ASMR episode! The episode only includes eating sounds of crispy chips. There is NO talking or whispering in this episode. Enjoy!

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
